in;\">8.3.Assumptions 18</p> <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\"><b>9.PARKING LOT ISSUES AND NEXT STEP 18</b></p> <p style=\"margin-left: 0.33in; margin-bottom: 0in;\">9.1.Parking Lot Issues 18</p> <p style=\"margin-left: 0.33in; margin-bottom: 0in;\">9.2.Next Step 18</p> <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\"><b>10.GENERIC ROLES AND RESPONSIBILITIES 19</b></p> <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\"><b>11.GLOSSARY OF TERMS 20</b></p> </div> <h1 class=\"western\" style=\"page-break-before: always;\"><font size=\"3\">DOCUMENT MANAGEMENT</font></h1> <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\"><br> </p> <ol><li><h3 class=\"western\"><font size=\"3\">Purpose</font></h3> </li></ol> <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\"><br> </p> <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\">The purpose of this document is to provide a mechanism for controlling the version releases of the Project Charter</p> <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\">.</p> <ol start=\"2\"><li><h3 class=\"western\"><font size=\"3\">Document Location</font></h3> </li></ol> <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\"><br> </p> <ol><ul><li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\">Each version of this document is to be treated as final until such time as a later release replaces it.</p> </li><li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\">All documents will be stored at  </p> </li><li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\">Only Project Resources and Stakeholders will have access to this folder.</p> </li></ul></ol> <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\"><br> </p> <ol start=\"3\"><li><h3 class=\"western\"><font size=\"3\">Revision History</font></h3> </li></ol> <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\"><br> </p> <table border=\"1\" bordercolor=\"#000000\" cellpadding=\"7\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"591\"> <col width=\"133\"> <col width=\"134\"> <col width=\"134\"> <col width=\"133\"> <tbody><tr valign=\"top\"> <td bgcolor=\"#bfbfbf\" width=\"133\"> <p><b>Document Version No.</b></p> </td> <td bgcolor=\"#bfbfbf\" width=\"134\"> <p><b>Revision Date</b></p> </td> <td bgcolor=\"#bfbfbf\" width=\"134\"> <p><b>Summary of 